{"tid":1423866,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"下禮一凌晨英仙座流星雨極大期","createTime":"2019-08-06T15:01:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T16:37:37.000Z","uid":298669,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0f0b43860e8a86d44eda1b39da97a99d66209eef","tid":1423866,"uid":298669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T15:01:47.000Z","msg":"下禮一凌晨 13/8 0:00 - 5:00 英仙座流星雨極大期<br />\n英仙座流星雨活躍期為  17/7 - 24/8<br />\n<br />\n今年8月13日，本港將有英仙座流星雨上演，高峰期間每小時天頂流星數量可達110顆。根據天文台建議，香港最佳觀賞時間在8月13日淩晨12am - 5am，有興趣的朋友要留意！<br />\n提提大家，要去遠離市區光害的郊區才能觀賞到流星雨，找一個較暗而視野廣闊的地方欣賞流星雨。亦有可能受天氣及月光影響，要視乎當日天氣狀況。 <br />\n<br />\n大家記得買足夠的裝備去觀星<br />\n電筒觀星筆少不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要影星星記的帶腳架<br />\n仲要記得帶裝備保護自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.lcsd.gov.hk/CE/Museum/Space/image/image_gallery-6157c988-71e7-425b-be89-a2ab4b91982b.html?uuid=6157c988-71e7-425b-be89-a2ab4b91982b&amp;groupId=2178963&amp;t=1484619903291\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lcsd.gov.hk%2FCE%2FMuseum%2FSpace%2Fimage%2Fimage_gallery-6157c988-71e7-425b-be89-a2ab4b91982b.html%3Fuuid%3D6157c988-71e7-425b-be89-a2ab4b91982b%26groupId%3D2178963%26t%3D1484619903291&h=5efc4a85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n圖片來源: 香港太空館"},{"pid":"a6c6a94647f1cfe7bb7d8c3c01408d509b2df043","tid":1423866,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:37:37.000Z","msg":"國之將亡必有異象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}